steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab list with name "Pages"
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT022d
Then I should see the screen with name JIT022d display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT022d
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT022d" with index "1"
When I add item "Text" without inputting in Search popup to preview mobile editor
Then I should see the preview mobile editor match with image title "JIT008.Search.Components.Text"
When I select item value "Text" with index "1"
When I update field label "Text" of header "Text" with value "JITERA new era in software development. New generation of coding, no code, save more time"
When I select the color for field label "Background Color" of header "Background" by inputting the hexcode value "FF0000"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT022d" with index "1"
